Later, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.

Career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries and remind attendees to maintain eye contact. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event, and a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. A whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews. In the background, a cybersecurity company runs a password cracking challenge on a laptop, while a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance. Groups of friends mark target employers on the event map.

Event staff scan registrations and distribute lanyards at the entrance, while human resources teams take notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. As students exit, they carry tote bags, a stack of business cards, and resumes in branded folders, accompanied by camera crews from the university media team capturing interviews. Career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. Meanwhile, healthcare providers showcase photos related to their community outreach efforts, and recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails. The dean visits the event to thank recruiters for their support of the university.

Some students use tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database, while human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. Career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries and remind attendees to maintain eye contact. An alumni panel discusses preparation for technical interviews, with representatives from nonprofits emphasizing mission-driven career paths. A cybersecurity company runs a password-cracking challenge on a laptop, and a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance. Nearby, alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station, and recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, with camera crews from the university media team capturing interviews during the event.
